    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Squirrel Away</strong> is your ticket to a <i>nutty</i> <i>adventure</i>! Enter a whimsical world where <strong>vintage arcade spirit </strong>merges with a <strong>quirky</strong>, <strong>modern</strong> approach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/04638ea42ab3b693086c73620ce42db9.poster.avif?t=1743747939\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/04638ea42ab3b693086c73620ce42db9.webm?t=1743747939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/04638ea42ab3b693086c73620ce42db9.mp4?t=1743747939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump</strong>, <strong>dodge</strong>, and <strong>climb</strong> your way through tricky levels as you hunt down acorns, outsmart sneaky foes, and race against the <strong>clock</strong>. It’s fast-paced fun with a twist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/2060871156453bd9e8ea2ec780ba9fca.poster.avif?t=1743747939\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/2060871156453bd9e8ea2ec780ba9fca.webm?t=1743747939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/2060871156453bd9e8ea2ec780ba9fca.mp4?t=1743747939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mix</strong> and <strong>mingle</strong> with the quirky locals of <strong>Pirate Town</strong>, dive into <strong>mini-quests</strong>, and try out unique gameplay challenges! There's always something wild waiting around the corner in this bustling, treasure-hunting haven.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/e9d1afbf5b6777bf1915474e49f49e9b.poster.avif?t=1743747939\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/e9d1afbf5b6777bf1915474e49f49e9b.webm?t=1743747939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/e9d1afbf5b6777bf1915474e49f49e9b.mp4?t=1743747939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join a band of mischievous squirrel thieves on the ultimate heist for the legendary golden acorn! Outsmart rival pirates, uncover hidden treasures, and explore a wacky island full of surprises and mini-games.<br> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/9b8278ecd3052777e9cdd92fbde44f1a.avif?t=1743747939\" width=252 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/97910b431f9d38b814d8e96b2283980a.poster.avif?t=1743747939\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205930/extras/97910b431f9d38b814d8e96b2283980a.webm?t=1743747939\